.<br>
.  I've been raised by good willing parents, who could go somewhat far in their studies but, money always getting in our legs while running to live, they couldn't.  Still, they were for me a source of information, being Why and How kid.  I still always ask why and how.<br>
<br>
.  When I graduated from High School, I ought to pay my studies for my 3-years technic in a &quot;CÉGEP&quot;.  In my province of Canada, Québec, the CÉGEP is just before the University.  CÉGEP means General and professional education college, or something like that.  Anyway, I took a job in a gas station.<br>
<br>
.  Man, I got down.  Pretty down.  All my life, I've been with the same friends, being used to be with intelligent people.  I cannot realize, after almost 2 years, how people can be stupid.<br>
<br>
